{"tid":387563,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有錢人家鍾意啲咩？","createTime":"2017-09-04T17:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T11:55:17.000Z","uid":33878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f197224fe4884359306c2c0bf16bf26be6e8b05a","tid":387563,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:12:15.000Z","msg":"佢地黎緊就七十歲生日&hellip;<br />\n係我父母啲親戚<br />\n佢地就住西九龍上蓋<br />\n我就屋邨窮撚一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地屋企受佢地屋企唔少恩惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我都好感激佢地 不過毒撚唔識多謝人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地成家黎緊就邀請我地一家去食佢地嘅生日飯<br />\n宜家諗緊送咩生日禮物比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋我地會去啲高級中式菜館食<br />\n究竟應該我地比定佢地比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我search 過一圍生日飯都成皮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地請又覺得好肉赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔請又要生日個邊比又唔多合理咁&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"0bc9d974c59173f9f815dfc01b56fa1a8ab52e16","tid":387563,"uid":1706,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:16:49.000Z","msg":"送d用錢買唔到既野囉<br />\n例如你整個蛋糕比佢地<br />\n同埋佢都知你地咩環境架啦，所以我覺得佢地未必會介意你地唔請"},{"pid":"074dc1656e5484932179037ac67f220cd716826f","tid":387563,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:27:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>送d用錢買唔到既野囉<br />\n例如你整個蛋糕比佢地<br />\n同埋佢都知你地咩環境架啦，所以我覺得佢地未必會介意你地唔請</blockquote><br />\n但係我只係一個毒撚<br />\n雖然我阿妹都幾識social<br />\n無神神整個蛋糕好似好噁心好作狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蛋糕我地買個Lady M 會唔會好啲 都成千蚊個 都叫有誠意呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9468fd9436da8a9353c6a454cfefaf595189dd8","tid":387563,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:31:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>送d用錢買唔到既野囉<br />\n例如你整個蛋糕比佢地<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同埋佢都知你地咩環境架啦，所以我覺得佢地未必會介意你地唔請</span></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗 事實真係咁<br />\n因為細個成日帶我地食自助餐都係佢地比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過宜家我大過左返緊工又好似唔同講法"},{"pid":"27cc9e92e198aa089517e7fe32d541d746e28d90","tid":387563,"uid":73,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:35:24.000Z","msg":"錢要買嘅佢地已經有<br />\n果日著得靚少少<br />\n自己整蛋糕, 睇下對方有冇糖尿<br />\n用健康食材<br />\n<br />\n請食飯就唔好, 食你一個月糧"},{"pid":"1b4420482d63da513d7fbf0705c3a04560f921b8","tid":387563,"uid":123663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:38:10.000Z","msg":"送茶葉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa3080c578d9f4e8ac42b34fff52b5a53690742c","tid":387563,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:40:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>送d用錢買唔到既野囉<br />\n例如你整個蛋糕比佢地<br />\n同埋佢都知你地咩環境架啦，所以我覺得佢地未必會介意你地唔請</blockquote><br />\n但係我只係一個毒撚<br />\n雖然我阿妹都幾識social<br />\n無神神整個蛋糕好似好噁心好作狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蛋糕我地買個Lady M 會唔會好啲 都成千蚊個 都叫有誠意呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁生日有蛋糕好正常啫<br />\n貴價蛋糕佢地無錢買咩，食死佢地都得啦<br />\n但你地一齊整既蛋糕佢地用成副身家都買唔到啦<br />\n誠意唔一定要用好多錢既<br />\n再畫張生日卡多謝佢地咁幫你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b147cd398702690a38c33b2d6e045ae059a077f2","tid":387563,"uid":13309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:42:56.000Z","msg":"老人家好蛋糕咩？買下靚生果/海味 佢地會知你心意架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be15b9ca0d9744977469f1d7c859b2934d628a8","tid":387563,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T18:04:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>送d用錢買唔到既野囉<br />\n例如你整個蛋糕比佢地<br />\n同埋佢都知你地咩環境架啦，所以我覺得佢地未必會介意你地唔請</blockquote><br />\n但係我只係一個毒撚<br />\n雖然我阿妹都幾識social<br />\n無神神整個蛋糕好似好噁心好作狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蛋糕我地買個Lady M 會唔會好啲 都成千蚊個 都叫有誠意呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁生日有蛋糕好正常啫<br />\n貴價蛋糕佢地無錢買咩，食死佢地都得啦<br />\n但你地一齊整既蛋糕佢地用成副身家都買唔到啦<br />\n誠意唔一定要用好多錢既<br />\n再畫張生日卡多謝佢地咁幫你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n整蛋糕同生日卡似比女朋友多啲wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋其實我同佢地好少傾計"},{"pid":"57f7406f7ec6fdf9a2acfa59219b1d883d59a32c","tid":387563,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T18:05:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>送茶葉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個有無咩推介 可以考慮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cded7bccfd644f55f82fabf2d3313348e267ecc","tid":387563,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T18:07:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錢要買嘅佢地已經有<br />\n果日著得靚少少<br />\n自己整蛋糕, 睇下對方有冇糖尿<br />\n用健康食材<br />\n<br />\n請食飯就唔好, 食你一個月糧</blockquote><br />\n我都諗住幫阿爸阿媽執執至去<br />\n佢地真係著得好求其<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有錢人真係特別注重健康"},{"pid":"9331354b3c1fa5d3c51bb33328a3a41bdbebf42c","tid":387563,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T18:08:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老人家好蛋糕咩？買下靚生果/海味 佢地會知你心意架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n海味都可以考慮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e94e0f462a77fae7d5e3b86773fc8bfdd8abf1d","tid":387563,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T03:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0dcfb1f1a3537cc6a22fd14bbd2f362c0f91be9","tid":387563,"uid":37064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T11:55:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}